{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01MwgQ4M3WDaQCqN1xaXN3ut","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01FoZSyUdnrRrjnWRMoiYrwQ","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/mydata/karma/runs/error-prone-rerun/elasticsearch-scale-certs-password-snapshot-audit-rollback-20260618_123155/stages/stage_03/submit.txt","content":"HTTP CA + leaf certificate rotation complete (no CRDs / ECK used).\n\nWhat was done:\n- Generated a NEW self-signed CA (CN=es-ca) and a NEW leaf cert (CN=es-http) signed\n  by it, both valid for 365 days (~1 year). Leaf SANs preserved exactly:\n  localhost, *.elasticsearch.svc, *.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local.\n\nRotation strategy (minimal downtime, the es-http-tls secret backs BOTH HTTP and\ntransport SSL for the `es` and `es-data` statefulsets):\n  Phase 1: patched secret es-http-tls ca.crt -> bundle(old CA + new CA) and waited\n           for the secret volume to propagate to all 5 pods. ES hot-reloads the\n           certificate_authorities file, so every node trusted both CAs before any\n           leaf change — no transport SSL break during the rollout.\n  Phase 2: patched tls.crt/tls.key -> new leaf, then rolling-restarted es-data and\n           es one pod at a time (cluster stayed green throughout).\n  Phase 3: trimmed ca.crt back to the new CA only (all leaves are new).\n\nClient trust:\n- Updated configmap es-http-ca to the new CA (ca.crt) for clients.\n- Verified a FULL TLS handshake (curl --cacert newCA, no -k) to\n  https://es-http.elasticsearch.svc:9200 -> http=200, ssl_verify_result=0.\n\nFinal state:\n- Cluster health: green, 5 nodes, 100% active shards.\n- Served leaf issuer=CN=es-ca, notAfter=Jun 18 2027 (new fingerprint).\n- New CA SHA256: BC:16:90:DA:2C:77:42:A5:44:B5:FB:DD:3D:C3:38:8B:4D:D4:E6:C0:2A:1F:69:8C:DE:A6:81:8F:A0:5A:C7:D4\n  (differs from baseline old CA E8:EA:51:...:9C:AB).\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":131,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1928,"cache_read_input_tokens":63900,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1928},"output_tokens":5,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5bdc8fd7-764d-4fa4-ab77-84fb412ac77d","uuid":"ce1cbabe-4d3c-4da6-bc60-3d22708e15d5","request_id":"req_011CcAnRseut1XVQZBNqKJyk"}
